    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin looks and smells brand new, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a complete service history and all components functioning exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new.",
